               <msContents>
                  <summary>Rampart of the Cross, ሐፁረ፡ መስቀል።</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="88r" facs="003">Fols 1r–88r</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5696MagicPrayer">Ḥaṣura
                                                  Masqal</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      ‎በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጽሐፍነ፡ ሐፁረ፡ መስቀል፡ ዘጸሐፈ፡ ኤርምያስ፡ ‎‎ነቢይ፡ ውስተ፡ ኰኵሕ፡ ታቦት፡ እም፬፡ አድባር፡ ወበውእቱ፡ ስም፡ ተምዓ፡ ‎‎ሞት፡ ወፆሩ፡ አጋንንት፡ ወአነሂ፡ ለገብርከ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>‎
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>
