                     <list>
                       <item xml:id="a1">
                         <locus target="#iir(ecto)" facs="002">Fol. iir(ecto)</locus>
                         <desc>
                           Excerpt from various prayers used as pen trials.</desc>
                         </item>
                       <item xml:id="a2">
                         <locus target="#iiv(ers0)" facs="003">Fol. iiv(ers0)</locus>
                         <desc>
                           Complaint of a scribe: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ም(ን)ተ፡ ኮንከ፡ አ(ን)ተ፡ እምትመጠው፡ ብርዕ፡ ሰናይ ዘፈተነ፡ ቀለመ፡ ጸሐፊሁ፡ ውእቱ፡ መዋቲ፡ ወልደ፡ ግሥሥ፡ ወመክርግ።</foreign>,
                           “What happened to you, Branna, that you do not receive the good pentrial which the scribe attempted with the ink.  The scribe is (merely) a mortal son!”  </desc>
                         </item>
